{"tid":1366667,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"南邊圍驚到咁不如暫定每個星期六都元朗遊行","createTime":"2019-07-26T04:28:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T07:36:51.000Z","uid":262322,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b1d6b63fc81da2f0ee46cf717303e2fd37ed5fc3","tid":1366667,"uid":262322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:28:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gjsT9xj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgjsT9xj.png&h=f09aacb9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f58e607e1e2ec11b9b20b68a2a3230aa1173e908","tid":1366667,"uid":45830,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:32:49.000Z","msg":"講真好多村民都多得班白衫唔少，持住黑社會搞事。"},{"pid":"fc1d114a71c8669cd7dde806178b2fb02924f59f","tid":1366667,"uid":289978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:35:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />使唔使叫林奠幫手圍水馬，由中聯辦圍到入元朗"},{"pid":"d6e651357cdc966dff74255cbb6374d48e6dd52c","tid":1366667,"uid":262322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc1d114a71c8669cd7dde806178b2fb02924f59f","tid":1366667,"uid":289978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:35:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />使唔使叫林奠幫手圍水馬，由中聯辦圍到入元朗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />圍晒成個香港"},{"pid":"b65ff7b52246e2f1e653303da8454068d612951b","tid":1366667,"uid":276548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:15:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>火燒南生圍 逾萬候鳥失棲息地</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有「雀鳥天堂」之稱的元朗南生圍，日前發生火災。山貝河近南生圍路的一幅草地突然起火，火種隨風勢蔓延至附近的蘆葦田，遊人發現後連忙報警。消防員到場後曾用山火拍撲救，但火場面積不斷擴大，並有3條長20米的火線。由於消防車無法駛近火場，加上火場面積廣闊，未能拖喉射水，最後政府飛行服務隊派出直升機投擲水彈協助。火警經17小時撲救後熄滅，4公頃的草地和林木被焚毀。消防員當時認為事件沒有可疑，於是收隊離開。<br />\n<br />\n然而，7小時後，南生圍的河邊草叢再次冒出濃煙，消防員到場後發現兩條約20米長的火線，飛行服務隊隨即派直升機擲水彈救火，至昨日傍晚才被救熄。消防指火警蔓延速度不尋常，認為起火原因有可疑，已交由警方進行調查。事後，漁護署亦派員前來查看，證實荒廢魚塘的塘壆和蘆葦牀被燒毀，以及少量樹木的樹幹底部被熏黑，但未發現有野生動物或候鳥傷亡。<br />\n<br />\n南生圍位於橫洲東面，被錦田河和山貝河包圍。南生圍的面積約70多公頃，其9成地方為濕地，內有紅樹林、魚塘、蘆葦叢和草地。每年有數以萬計的候鳥棲息，吸引本港和外地觀鳥人士到來觀察和研究。假日期間也有不少巿民到來郊遊、踏單車和寫生等，享受大自然景色，因此南生圍又稱為「港人後花園」。"},{"pid":"827b2a5ebebcbc69a3cf0dbc61ec1c059fa1b6d3","tid":1366667,"uid":20209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:17:15.000Z","msg":"木板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小心着火呀"},{"pid":"e7cf7112a11f22f7a0c969cf3847bd141c1b6406","tid":1366667,"uid":276548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"827b2a5ebebcbc69a3cf0dbc61ec1c059fa1b6d3","tid":1366667,"uid":20209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:17:15.000Z","msg":"木板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小心着火呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:20:48.000Z","msg":"天氣咁熱 易燃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a061d4901ea71bf93513ccd746f7b6bc55d9aca8","tid":136